decks.notes: The key concept of this deck is to quickly and efficiently assemble the necessary cards to execute the Tameshi Bloom combo. This includes using cards like Lotus Bloom and Wargate to generate mana, while also utilizing Teferi, Time Raveler to control the game and protect the combo. The deck also incorporates cards like Eladamri's Call and Finale of Devastation to search for specific combo pieces. Additionally, it includes various lands and utility cards to support the overall game plan.
